# Agentic Farm Export Ignore List (v1.0)
# [Intent] Defines files to be excluded from /exprj while maintaining management capability in the root.

# 1. Management Harnesses (Layer 1 - Stay in Root)
.agent/
.worktrees/
.superpowers/
docs/log/
docs/superpowers/plans/
GEMINI.md
Strategy of Container Identification and Naming.md

# 2. Transient Operational Data
shared-context/*.log
shared-context/*.blocked
shared-context/*.tmp
orchestrator/.env

# 3. Environment Specifics
node_modules/
dashboard/dist/
*.ps1
